1.plot: When Autumn and Ash's relationship goes viral, things take a turn on the set. All attention is placed on Autumn's relationship causing tension among the palette. Meanwhile, Amber shows a softer side.

3.title: I've Got a Friend
3.plot: After moving to LA from South Dakota, Autumn, sweet and innocent, at her first day of makeup internship, is surprised by some of the people she meets and learns her new job could be a bit more complicated than anticipated.

4.title: Scarred
4.plot: Everyone is anxiously waiting to hear about the Time Warp Tour getting renewed.. Autumn and Violet underestimate Tawny and learn to value her more as a friend and makeup artist. Ash reveals his true feelings for Autumn in a surprising way.

5.title: Back Where I Belong
5.plot: Autumn is settling into her new life and attempting to come to grips with her feelings for Ash. Things quickly go awry when Autumn meets Jade, a guest on Time Warp Tour, which causes drama in both Autumn's love and work life.

6.title: White Lies
6.plot: As Autumn and Ash's relationship progresses, Autumn realizes her feelings have changed. Chris Duarte, a special guest on Time Warp Tour, causes a lot of excitement both at work and at home.

7.title: I Pray
7.plot: Tawny's grades fall, so Autumn and Violet use some innovative actors on the Time Warp Tour set to help Tawny study. Cerise and Uncle Hue face the loss of their father. Autumn acts out after being told she can't attend Papa's funeral.

imdb.plot outline: "Painting Autumn" is a live action sitcom featuring actress Hannah Paschke as a makeup artist named Autumn Farve. Autumn is a popular beauty vlogger, who scores the internship of a lifetime, working in the makeup department for "Time Warp Tour", the most popular teen show on television. Autumn soon finds out that living her dream in Hollywood means accepting all the drama that comes with it. Through vlogging, her own creativity, and relying on her palette of friends, Autumn dazzles everyone in LA with her small town values and her heart of gold.
